Release Notes:

For fans of Whitesnake, Skid Row, Shotgun Messiah. DYNAZTY*s "Bring The Thunder" was recorded at Polar studios in Stockholm, Sweden under the hands of producer Chis Laney (ZAN CLAN, ANIMAL) This thunderous heavy metal group dominated the Swedish live scene with its flamboyant shows and powerful anthems for many months before hooking up with producer Chris Laney to record a debut album. For one month Dynazty worked with Laney creating a fierce album that will make a lasting impression. DYNAZTY features Rob Love, a former guitar slinger in ZAN CLAN along with Chis Laney.
